Good dueling tips:<br>
~Buy alot of pumice and hot key it. <br>
~DS potion if you can, but more than likely you'll get dispelled.(See pumice)<br>
~Have a large two-hand weapon in case they start to cheese on you and try jousting.<br>
~Don't forget ranged weapons, if they start to run around when hurt, plink them.<br>
~If its warrior on warrior, just stand your ground, if they try straffing, just turn in circles with them.<br>
~Don't forget your /dis, know which to use in which case. Reposte &gt; Mighty strike <br>
~Don't forget disarm during duels, both for you and against you.<br>
<br>
See I told you alot more than I should have, but hell its fun to duel. <p><br>
